quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"Maaku : \"Wahayinaama e am, wonnde dental jinna he…óino [lam mi…óo jannga Alqur'aana], …ói wi'i: \"Menen men nani janngeteende haawniinde"
  72,2,"Hinde …óowira e peewal. Men gom…óinii nde. Men kafidatah e Joomi amen, hay e gooto"
  72,3,"E wonnde manngural Joomi amen ngal mawnii, O siforaali jogitagol genndo, wanaa …ìi…ó…óo"
  72,4,"E wonnde [Ibuliisa] …óay…óo on e amen hino wowlaynoo penaale e hoore Allah"
  72,5,Menen men sikkuno wonnde yim…ìe e jinna wowlataano fenaande e hoore Allah
  72,6,"Hari le wor…ìe yim…ìe hino mooloraynoo wor…ìe jinna, …ìe …ìeydi …ói bewre"
  72,7,"Kam…ìe [yim…ìe …ìen] …ìe sikkir no sikkir…óon non, wonnde Allah immintintah hay gooto"
  72,8,"E wonnde men meemii kammu ngun, men tawi hingu hebbiniraa aynoo…ìe tii…óu…ìe e docote"
  72,9,"E wonnde me…óen joo…óotonoo ton fii he…óagol. Kala non he…óitii…óo jooni, o hawray e docotal tommbingal"
  72,10,"E wonnde men anndaa si ko bone faandanaa won…ìe ka leydi …ìen, kaa hara Joomi ma…ì…ìe faandani …ìe peewal"
  72,11,"E wonnde hino e amen mo∆¥∆¥u…ói, hino e amen kadi ko jaasi …óum. Hari me…óen e laawi seertu…ói"
  72,12,"E wonnde men fellituno men laawotaako Allah ka hoore leydi, e wonnde men laawortaa Mo dogugol"
  72,13,"E wonnde nde men nanunoo peewal nagl, men gom…óini ngal. Kala gom…óin…óo Joomi mun, on hulataa …óuytaneede [mo∆¥∆¥i] wanaa …ìeydaneede [bon…ói]"
  72,14,"E wonnde hino e amen jebbilii…ói, hino e amen kadi oo√±ii…ói. Kala jebbilii ngii, …óin …óon faandike peewal"
  72,15,"Oo√±ii…ói …óin kan, …ói laatanike Jahannama on carmalle"
  72,16,"E wonnde si …ìe √±ii…ìuno e hoore laawol ngol, ko pellet, Men yarnayno …ìe ndiyam …óuu…óu…óam"
  72,17,"fii yo Men ndaarndoro …ìe heen. Kala …óuurnii…óo e jantoore Joomi mun nden, O naaday mo e lette sattu…óe"
  72,18,E wonnde juulir…óe …óen ko Allah heeranii. Wata on kafidu e Allah hay e gooto
  72,19,"E wonnde tuma jeyaa…óo Allah on darinoo himo rewa Mo, …ói …óe…ìuno wa…ó…óondirgol e hoore makko"
  72,20,"Maaku : \"Anndee ko Joomi am (tun) mi rewata, mi kafidataa Mo kadi hay e gooto"
  72,21,"Maaku : \"Min on mi waawanaa on du√±ude lorra, wanaa fii poo…óugol nafa"
  72,22,"Maaku : \"Hay gooto waawaa da…óndugol lam e Allah; mi he…ìataa ko woori Mo ∆¥oo√±orde"
  72,23,"si wanaa yottingol immorde e Allah e nule Makko …óen. Kala yeddu…óo Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, haray ko Yiite Jahannama woodani mo, …ìe luttay e magge poomaa"
  72,24,"Haa si …ìe yi'ii ko …ìe kammbirananoo kon, …ìe aray anndude ko hombo …ìuri lo'ude ballo, …ìuri kadi fan…óude limoore"
  72,25,"Maaku : \"Mi anndaa si ko kammbirana…óon kon hino …ìadii, maa si Joomi am wa…óanay …óum dumunna"
  72,26,Ko O ganndo wirnii…ói. O ∆¥ellintinantaa wirnii…ói Makko …óin hay e gooto
  72,27,"si wanaa mo O welanaa e Nulaa…óo, O naadnay yeeso on e …ìaawo makko tommbotoo…ìe"
  72,28,"fii yo o anndu wonnde …ìen yottinii nule Joomi ma…ì…ìe …óen. O hu…ìindorii (anndugol) ko woni ka ma…ì…ìe kon, O mofti limoore kala huunde"
  73,1,"Ko an yo buumor…óo [comci mun]"
  73,2,"∆Åa≈ão (wuurnitaa) jemma on, si wanaa see…óa [e makko]"
  73,3,"feccere makko, maa …óuytaa see…óa e …óum"
  73,4,maa …ìeydaa …óon. Janngiraa Alqur'aanaare nden rewnindiral
  73,5,Me…óen saatii tellinnde e maa…óa konngol teddungol
  73,6,"Pellet, ko dewal tummbo jemma ngal, …ìuri tii…óude batte e fooccaade konngol"
  73,7,"Anndu hino woodan-maa e √±alorma on, ferlitagol juutungol"
  73,8,"Janto innde Joomi maa nden, ta∆¥o-…óaa yahaa e Makko hattirde ta∆¥agol"
  73,9,"Jey…óo On fu…ónaange e hiirnaange.Rewetee…óo woo alaa e si nwona Kanko,Jogito Mo hoolortee…óo"
  73,10,Mu√±√±o e ko …ìe wowlata kon; wo…ó…óito-raa …ìe wo…ó…óitannde labaande
  73,11,Accidam e fennoo…ìe joomiraa…ìe neemaaji …ìen; habbito-…óaa …ìe see…óa
  73,12,"Ko pellet, hino ka Amen gaa : Tonngii e Jahiimi"
  73,13,"e √±aametee …óe…ó…óoowo, e lette muusu…óe"
  73,14,"√ëalnde leydi ndin e pelle …óen dillata, pelle …óen wa'a wa njaare ilayndi"
  73,15,Min nelii e mon nelaa…óo haa o wona seede e dow mon hono no Min nelduno faade e Fir*awna Nelaa…óo
  73,16,Fir*awna woopi nelaa…óo O Min nanngi mbo nanngugol cattungol
  73,17,Hono ndeenraton pittaali mon si on yeddi √±alawmo ba…óoowo sukaa…ìe danndalinde
  73,18,Kammu o na fetti e kulhuli hembo laatiima fodoore Alla ko wonoore
  73,19,Ko oon woni waaju goongo kala faalaa…óo da…óde nanngira joomiiko ruttorde